messages.message: @Matt posting here for knowledge share. Here’s a flow that does “Data Quality issue”: https://www.instabase.com/apps/flow/results/dlluncor/tests/fs/Test%20Drive/tests/general/single-flows/samples/review-validate/out/batch.ibflowresults. Click on “Link” under the table and you’ll see the issue, you can correct it, and then re-validate. The flow to run this is here: https://www.instabase.com/apps/flow/edit/dlluncor/tests/fs/Test%20Drive/tests/general/single-flows/workflows/review-validate.ibflow# (use Flow Binary)
